import React from 'react'
import Button from '@mui/material/Button'
import DeleteIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Delete'
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography';
import { Container, Grid, TextField } from '@mui/material';
import Paper from '@mui/material/Paper';


function Login () {
return <>

<Grid container>
    <Grid item xs={0} sm={600} md={900} lg={1200} xl={1536}>

    <Container align="center" id="Cont" marginTop="150px" >
    <Paper background-color="white" square={false} elevation={0}>
    <Typography variant="h5" component="h5" >Acceder</Typography>
    <TextField  id="usuario" type='' variant="outlined" helperText="Inserte el usuario"/>
    <TextField  id="contraseña" variant="outlined" label="Contraseña" type='password'/>

    </Paper>

    </Container>

    
    </Grid>














</Grid>
</>
}
export default Login
